                <h3><a href="/jobs/community-jobs-scotland/vacancies/p19v">16–29 year olds</a></h3>
                <p>
                  The following vacancies are only open to vulnerable unemployed 16 to 29 year olds, including <strong>carers</strong>, <strong>early service leavers (armed forces)</strong>, <strong>care experienced</strong>, <strong>disabled</strong> and <strong>young people with convictions</strong> who are not on the Work Programme, Work Choice, Specialist Employment Support, Work First Scotland or Work Able Scotland.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4">
                <h3><a href="/jobs/community-jobs-scotland/vacancies/aag">16–19 years old on an Activity Agreement</a></h3>
                <p>
                  The following vacancies are only open to unemployed 16 to 19 year olds who are currently participating on an Activity Agreement.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="mdc-layout-grid__cell mdc-layout-grid__cell--span-4">
                <h3><a href="/jobs/community-jobs-scotland/vacancies/p52">16–29 year olds with a disability</a></h3>
                <p>
                  The following vacancies are only open to unemployed 16 to 29 year olds who have a disability and or long term health condition and <strong>who are not</strong> on the Work Programme, Community Work Placement, Work Choice or Specialist Employment Support
                </p>
